name: It's s Five O'Clock Somewhere...
description:
A peak experience at 5 a.m, where a moment of oneness. Where everything fell into place and where are dreams are obtainable.

Ever since that moment it had been my journey to explore what that feeling was via the arts. 

I want digital talisman inspire and be an anthem for the people around the world, wanting to start each day with energy, gusto sunshine and that life on this day go perfectly as they they imagine it to be.
